{"id": 1579, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得情侣之间有哪些感情试金石？", "description": "找对象千年等一回，但如果经不起这些考验，情感破裂简直就是分分钟的事。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 4958, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322112625SPAvx0mCEKUlQdWN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-23T03:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 182784, "content": "财政大权谁把握！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979884}, {"id": 183040, "content": "对视", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980511}, {"id": 184320, "content": "所谓试金石就是全靠对方有多稀罕自己罢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983683}, {"id": 182785, "content": "一起狼人杀..", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979885}, {"id": 183041, "content": "想到要试就不该在一起。决定在一起就别想试。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980602}, {"id": 182786, "content": "是否愿意交流自己对我们的未来的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891733}, {"id": 183042, "content": "狼人杀胜率都百分之九十，让我怎么相信你?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964963}, {"id": 185602, "content": "对对，不要试\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987375}, {"id": 182787, "content": "互相看一次手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969621}, {"id": 183043, "content": "没必要试", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600658}, {"id": 187139, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985401}, {"id": 195331, "content": "一起吃个饭就能看出来啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011062}, {"id": 182788, "content": "他在你面前提起其他女生", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979894}, {"id": 183044, "content": "距离？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980609}, {"id": 198149, "content": "前爱慕对象。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011736}, {"id": 182789, "content": "你用谎言去验证谎言得到的一定是谎言", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947348}, {"id": 183045, "content": "把家门钥匙给你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925003}, {"id": 182790, "content": "时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617465}, {"id": 183046, "content": "会互相理解对方?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979243}, {"id": 182791, "content": "遇到不同问题的解决方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969199}, {"id": 183047, "content": "不互相信任", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972580}, {"id": 182792, "content": "1.不允許你想做的事，要求你不喜歡做的事。\n2.暴力侵向。\n3.承諾像開空頭支票，永遠不兌現不了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978326}, {"id": 183048, "content": "心里有对方\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832979}, {"id": 183049, "content": "心里有对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832979}, {"id": 184073, "content": "长胖二十斤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026193}, {"id": 182794, "content": "感情，还是不要去刻意考验的好。既然不信那也就不用考验了；相信，那也不需要考验了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911874}, {"id": 183050, "content": "问你爱不爱我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926970}, {"id": 182795, "content": "重大疾病，包括抑郁症。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 888133}, {"id": 183051, "content": "这个问题就是?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925400}, {"id": 183563, "content": "周末早上，两个人都还还赖在床上时，会不会下楼去买煎饼果子给我吃?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981803}, {"id": 182796, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865325}, {"id": 183052, "content": "贫穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970315}, {"id": 182797, "content": "交换社交软件密码㊙️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958290}, {"id": 184845, "content": "T戴与否.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984841}, {"id": 182798, "content": "遇到问题，关于各种事情，能否以及愿意彼此坦诚相待，能否真诚地交流，能否彼此包容谅解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962900}, {"id": 183054, "content": "下面每个看一遍，记住，别犯贱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766476}, {"id": 187150, "content": "一吵架就知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991833}, {"id": 182799, "content": "这就是个伪命题、钱能试出一切答案、就看你能不能接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117384}, {"id": 183055, "content": "一个人做菜，另一个就要刷碗！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759666}, {"id": 183056, "content": "性爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742448}, {"id": 183057, "content": "无意之间听到的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529205}, {"id": 188689, "content": "时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995155}, {"id": 183058, "content": "时间+金钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980642}, {"id": 182803, "content": "试居?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791893}, {"id": 190227, "content": "千万别试", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000450}, {"id": 197141, "content": "异地恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016135}, {"id": 182805, "content": "对生活的期待", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978830}, {"id": 183061, "content": "滥用各种社交账号\n对彼此没有用心地坦诚\n总是提起前任及初恋无论是好话还是坏话\n不会好好照顾自己\n不够努力不够上进总是想依赖\n  \n\n嗯异国。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978294}, {"id": 183573, "content": "不作不死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981846}, {"id": 182807, "content": "異地戀吧 很辛苦 總會亂七八糟瞎想 動不動就絕望：完了我們可能不合適要不分手吧別折磨了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643161}]}